    "definitions": [
      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "warm soba noodles (esp. for dipping, either served after being boiled, or cooled and then rewarmed)",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "寒い冬の昼下がり、湯気の上がる熱盛りそばを注文して暖を取る。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「あつあつ」の熱盛りそばを、鰹出汁の効いた辛口のつゆでいただく。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "蕎麦の風味を存分に楽しみたいなら、冷やしよりも熱盛りそばを好む人も多い。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「すみません、せいろを一枚、熱盛りそばでいただけますか」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "熱盛りそばは、麺同士がくっつきやすいため、供されたらすぐに手早く手繰るのが粋とされる。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "茹でたての蕎麦を一度冷水で締め、再び湯通しして提供される熱盛りそばは、独特の食感がある。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      }
